19:45.048 --> 19:46.831
If you and Leonard
get back together,

19:46.833 --> 19:48.333
Sheldon and I
will finally have someone

19:48.335 --> 19:50.018
to go on double dates with.

19:50.020 --> 19:51.336
What about me and Howard?

19:51.338 --> 19:53.772
Fine, we can double
with you, too.

19:54.657 --> 19:56.975
So insecure.

19:58.114 --> 20:00.865
Where are you guys going to eat?

20:00.867 --> 20:03.684
Penny?

20:05.037 --> 20:10.207
Do you, Penny, take Leonard to
be your lawful wedded husband?

20:17.549 --> 20:19.266
Well, it's
a little late for me

20:19.268 --> 20:21.552
to start saying no,
isn't it?

20:23.055 --> 20:25.056
Penny.

20:25.058 --> 20:26.173
Sorry,
just remembered

20:26.175 --> 20:28.025
I've got to stop
at the drugstore.

